{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_07_02",
  "title": "井川葵 2話 かっこ良く斬られてほしいな",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "え？　葵の演技の練習に？　俺が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Me‚ for your acting practice‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、付き合ってほしいんだ\n他のメンバーは、別の仕事でいないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I want you to help me out.\nThe other members are out on other jobs‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.0999998092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "さとみは忙しそうだし\n今、空いてるのは君だけだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi seems busy‚\nand you're the only one free right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2666660944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら演技指導のコーチを呼んだ方がいいんじゃ……\nあと、俺だって暇な訳じゃないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shouldn’t we call an acting coach or something…\nAnd it’s not like I have nothing better to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0666660944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、いいじゃないか。本格的な演技はまた今度\nまずは感覚を掴みたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ it’ll be fine. We can do serious practice later.\nI just want to get a feel for it right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4666662215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "イメージトレーニングみたいなものだから\n大袈裟に考えないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like brain training‚\nso don't overthink it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7666662215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "――君は、僕を信じて\nただ斬られてくれればいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――You just need to trust me\nand let yourself be slain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.400001335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え……お、おい、まさか練習って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… W-wait‚ you’re not saying the practice is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6624498526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "刀を使ったアクションシーンの練習がしたいんだ\n僕が斬る役。君は斬られる役",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to practice an action scene with swords.\nI’m the one who slays‚ you’re the one who gets slain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8000000635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "――どうせなら、かっこ良く斬られてほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――I’d like you to be slain in style‚ if you don’t mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.374985965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いやいやいや！　俺はそういう経験はないし\nやっぱり、ちゃんとした演技指導の人をだな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ no‚ no! I have no experience with that‚\nwe should definitely get someone who can teach us properly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333313623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そこにスポーツチャンバラ用の刀を用意してあるから\nはい、構えて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've prepared a foam weapon over there‚\nso get ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5999975204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "頼むから俺の話を聞いてくれ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ just listen to me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7767499925,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3616.276741099995,
          "startTime": 67.3930267336
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "胴！　と見せかけて、面！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Body! Just kidding‚ head!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1367409232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あたっ！？　いきなりフェイントをかけないでくれ\nそもそも俺はどう動けばいいんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ow!? Don’t suddenly feint!\nHow am I supposed to move in the first place!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2999860765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ここで一句\n鳴かぬなら、鳴くまで斬ろうホトトギス",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A verse for you.\nIf it doesn’t sing‚ I’ll slay it until it does‚ cuckoo bird.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5666573209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "一句じゃなくてセリフを読んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Read the lines‚ not a verse!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2475184206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "セリフは……なんだっけ、忘れちゃった。まぁいいや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The lines… What were they? I forgot. Whatever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7541891182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "全然良くない。……なぁ葵、もしかして遊んでないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not okay at all… Hey Aoi‚ are you messing with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2631902461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないでしょ、大事な役なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would never! It’s an important role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4402394062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだよな、ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah‚ you’re right. Sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7301712917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "でも君が相手だと\nどうしても遊んでる感じになっちゃうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ with you as my partner‚\nit inevitably feels like you're just messing around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1333229704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺が悪いのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it my fault…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1042450831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ細かいことはいいから\n今はイメージトレーニングっていうことで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ let’s not worry about the details.\nJust think of it as brain training for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5333209358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "――君は、僕を信じて\nただ斬られてくれればいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――You just need to trust me\nand let yourself be slain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2666542692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それ、さっきも言ってたけど\nいいセリフみたいに言ってもダメだからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said that before‚ but\nit doesn’t work if you’re just saying it like it’s a cool line!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9999876025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、今一つイメージが掴めないな\n今度は君から斬りかかってみてくれない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I’m still not getting the feel of it.\nWhy don’t you try attacking me this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6333219531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "僕がそれを避けて、後ろから斬りつけるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll dodge it and then slash you from behind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8661626899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いいけど……もうフェイントは勘弁してくれよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ but… No more feinting‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3981284702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "――正体を知られた以上\n生かして帰す訳にはいかない。覚悟して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Now that you know my true identity‚\nI can't let you leave here alive. Prepare yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_02-koh013.m4a",
